title: Wonderful 2 bedroom 2 bathroom, with amazing 15th floor city views
posting_body: ['%&&Wonderful 2 bedroom 2 bathroom, with amazing 15th floor city views!', 'Available immediately .', 'Features rare European Oak wood floors, black stainless steel appliances, granite counter tops, floor to ceiling impact windows, private balcony w/ glass railings, slide out kitchen pantry drawers, ample master bathroom storage space, walk-in closets in both bedrooms & a washer/dryer in unit.', 'Resort style amenities include: Fitness center, 2 infinity edged pools, steam rooms, theatre room, club room, party room, pool table & lounge.', '24 hour concierge & valet parking.', "Located in coveted downtown Brickell, walking distance to Brickell City Center, Mary Brickell Village & right in the heart of Miami's finest dining, shopping & night life!%&$", '#$%If you have been denied an application for lease in the past due to bad credit or your background, please call me or text me', 'show contact info', ', I will get you approved!!', 'Self-employed, bad credit, no problem.', 'Text me, I respond immediately and have tons of inventory!', 'WE ARE ESSENTIAL BUSINESS FOR COVI19, WE ARE ALWAYS OPEN', 'CALL ME OR TEXT ME', 'Andy Zamudio', 'show contact info', 'We accept deposits with credit card if you are short of cash we help with that, we are the only company that accepts credit cards for deposits , zelle, cash app, paypal venmo payments accepted!!!', 'Aceptamos los depositos con tarjeta de credito sinud esta corto de cash, somos la unica compañia que lo acepta en Florida, zelle, cash app, paypal ,venmo.']
